  "mime": {
    "text/plain": "s is a raw conversion from a Google Doc (link to original Google Doc).\nDocs to Markdown (gd2md-html) sample/demo doc\nThis page demonstrates the features of gd2md-html conversion from a Google Doc to a simple Markdown or HTML file. \n\nNote: Not all Markdown renderers support all Markdown features. For example github Markdown does not support a table of contents ([TOC]), footnotes, or definition lists. Also, some Markdown environments strip heading IDs and replace them with their own generated IDs. You’ll have to do some manual adjustments, depending on your target environment.\n\nHeadings\nHeading IDs\nBasic paragraphs\nMixed code spans\nLists\nNumbered lists\nOrdered lists\nLists with code blocks\nDefinition lists\nDefinition list examples\nCode blocks\nCode blocks with lang specification\nTables\nLinks\nImages\nDrawings\nEquations\nRight-to-left text\nSubscript and superscript processing\nBugs\n",
    "text/html": "<meta charset=\"utf-8\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-ba998808-7fff-08a1-a0c9-957f389ddfae\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">s is a raw conversion from a Google Doc (</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">link to original Google Doc</span></a><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">).</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Roboto,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Docs to Markdown (gd2md-html) sample/demo doc</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">This page demonstrates the features of gd2md-html conversion from a Google Doc to a simple Markdown or HTML file.&nbsp;</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Note</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: Not all Markdown renderers support all Markdown features. For example github Markdown does not support a table of contents (</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[TOC]</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">), footnotes, or definition lists. Also, some Markdown environments strip heading IDs and replace them with their own generated IDs. You’ll have to do some manual adjustments, depending on your target environment.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/edit#heading=h.x1tvnl5f0dml\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Headings</span></a></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/edit#heading=h.w9shf4dpypi9\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Heading IDs</span></a></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/edit#heading=h.g1bp6exwrddo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Basic paragraphs</span></a></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/edit#heading=h.7h6grt4spozt\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Mixed code spans</span></a></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KdK7bIKoOnUeuWAbloDYkLpBttaH22u-wQ9z85Ec0lo/edit#heading=h.a3od7xurwx1r\" style=\"text-decoration:n